  "title": "Insurance Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Advisory & Sales:</strong> Assess client needs, analyze risk profiles, and recommend appropriate insurance solutions (e.g., life, health, general).</li><li><strong>Relationship Management:</strong> Build long-term relationships, providing high-quality service and, in some cases, mentoring junior staff.</li><li><strong>Client Servicing:</strong> Assist with policy administration, renewals, and claims processing to ensure a smooth experience.</li><li><strong>Product Knowledge:</strong> Maintain in-depth knowledge of insurance products, regulations, and market trends.</li><li><strong>Goal Achievement:</strong> Drive business targets by collaborating with partners and sales teams. </li></ul>",
